title: Navigating the Common Challenges of Marriage, Part 7
itunes:author: John Fuller & Greg Smalley
itunes:summary: Raising children can be one of the most joyful experiences in your life, but it will forever change the dynamics of your marriage. Greg, Erin and John share some ideas for making time for your spouse, while raising small children.
